    "text": "focusing on kubernetes related work",
    "start": "31519",
    "end": "35280"
  },
  {
    "text": "thanks nick",
    "start": "35280",
    "end": "36960"
  },
  {
    "text": "today we will talk about how to keep",
    "start": "36960",
    "end": "39840"
  },
  {
    "text": "persistent volumes healthy for stay for",
    "start": "39840",
    "end": "42879"
  },
  {
    "text": "workloads",
    "start": "42879",
    "end": "45840"
  },
  {
    "text": "here is today's agenda",
    "start": "46239",
    "end": "48879"
  },
  {
    "text": "we will first talk about what problems",
    "start": "48879",
    "end": "51120"
  },
  {
    "text": "we could encounter after voting is",
    "start": "51120",
    "end": "53600"
  },
  {
    "text": "provisioned",
    "start": "53600",
    "end": "55280"
  },
  {
    "text": "then we will introduce the volume health",
    "start": "55280",
    "end": "57920"
  },
  {
    "text": "monitor feature",
    "start": "57920",
    "end": "60000"
  },
  {
    "text": "we will give a demo of the existing",
